    <title>Maintain SSL Certificates on Activation Node</title>
    <prolog>
        <source/>
        <permissions view="ericsson_internal"/>
        <metadata>
            <keywords>
                <keyword/>
            </keywords>
            <othermeta content="NA" name="workitem"/>
        </metadata>
        <resourceid appid="NA" ux-source-priority="topic-and-map"/>
    </prolog>
    <conbody>
        <p>Certificates for SSL verification are time-limited, therefore you must check the validity
            of all installed SSL certificates. SSL certificates with validity dates shorter than one
            year must be replaced during an appropriate maintenance window.</p>
        <p>This section describes how to maintain three types of certificates:<ul id="ul_dlk_2r2_kjb">
                <li>
                    <p>Puppet certificates</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p>Internal certificates for communication within the cluster</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p>External certificates for communication outside the cluster</p>
                </li>
            </ul></p>
    </conbody>
</concept>